    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\ude97 You honestly won't believe how gorgeous this car is. It\u2019s been my absolute baby and looks like it just rolled off the showroom floor\u2014truly a rare find! It\u2019s in flawless condition, drives like a dream, and has been pampered every single day. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s basically brand new without the dealership price tag, this is the one for you. Come take a look, you\u2019re going to fall in love!",
