    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "Available is an investment-grade E92 M3, a pinnacle of naturally aspirated engineering. This specimen features the S65 4.0L V8, utilizing individual throttle bodies and a high-pressure Vanos system to achieve a linear power delivery up to its 8,400 RPM redline. Power is managed via a 7-speed M-DCT dual-clutch transmission and a variable M-differential lock for optimal torque distribution. The chassis is equipped with Electronic Damper Control (EDC) providing exceptional lateral stiffness and damping precision. This vehicle is mechanically synchronized, with documented preventive maintenance on rod bearings and throttle actuators. The exterior retains its factory depth and luster, while the cabin's Novillo leather remains in showroom condition with no bolster compression. A turn-key example for the technical purist.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
